isbn 1 - 56563-860-3 ) , in the bible , was the name of a village near jerusalem—see bethany ( biblical village)—mentioned in the new testament as the home of the siblings mary , martha , and lazarus , and , according to the gospel of john , the site of a miracle in which jesus raises lazarus from the dead .

going to ... : jesus went from bethany to this city where he had his last meal

jerusalem